				<h2>Description:</h2>
				<p>
					This website is my first project for learning <a href="https://nodejs.org/">Node.js</a> .<br>
					The technologies and some tools used to construct this site are listed in the section below.<br><br>

					The information pertinent to the recipes shown on this website, such as recipe names, descriptions,
					ingredients,
					ingredient images, and preparing instructions, are fetched from the <a
						href="https://spoonacular.com/food-api">Spoonacular</a> food and recipes API.<br><br>

					Since I don't have control over the information that my application receives from the Spoonacular
					API, I decided to filter
					it and remove a set of words and terms related to allergies and special diets, such as "gluten free"
					and "lacto ovo vegetarian".
					The terms I remove from Spoonacular's content are replaced by asterisk (*) characters.<br><br>

					<b class="text-danger">This website was built with the only purposes of learning and entertainment.
						We do not recommend you to prepare any food based on the recipes presented here.</b><br><br>

					If you have any comments or suggestions about this website, want to suggest some improvement for the
					project or its source code,
					or if you find something strange or an error/bug, please contact me by email or open an issue on the
					<a href="https://github.com/jpgmoreira/recipe-finder">project's page on GitHub</a>.<br><br>

					Have fun :)
				</p>
